fields.headline: Genius No 156
fields.bodyText: Eleven clues are identically deficient in their cryptic component, reflecting the passing of the solution to one of them. Deadline for entries is 23:59 GMT on Saturday 2 July. You need to register once and then sign in to theguardian.com to enter our online competition for a £100 monthly prize. Click here to register. The deadline for entering this month’s competition has now passed.
